Instead of wondering, run:

Minimum Signal Test

Take one piece of your system and:
	1.	Explain it simply
	2.	Give a clear use case
	3.	Show a concrete result
	4.	Share it with 3–5 people
	5.	Observe:
	•	Do they understand it?
	•	Do they use it?
	•	Do they care?

⸻

Outcomes:
	•	❌ No engagement → refine clarity
	•	⚠️ Partial → improve framing
	•	✅ Strong → scale it

